berarti saling menguntungkan.

109
00:16:36,656 --> 00:16:39,573
Jika tak suka orang kami,
lalu apa usulmu?

110
00:16:39,823 --> 00:16:41,395
Pria bernama Hathaway.

111
00:16:42,124 --> 00:16:43,160
Dia seorang peretas...

112
