126
00:17:37,859 --> 00:17:39,604
...kepala pembuat programnya?

127
00:17:40,131 --> 00:17:41,374
Nicholas Hathaway.

128
00:17:41,534 --> 00:17:42,708
Benar.

129
00:17:43,471 --> 00:17:46,790
Peretas menemukan RAT daring
dan mengubahnya.

130
00:17:47,446 --> 00:17:49,397
Jika ingin memeriksa program ini...

131
00:17:49,551 --> 00:17:51,297
...mencari petunjuk identitas peretasnya...

132
00:17:51,456 --> 00:17:53,633
...kita butuh penciptanya.

133
00:18:28,903 --> 00:18:31,212
