965
01:59:39,426 --> 01:59:41,440
Ini bukan soal uang.

966
01:59:44,103 --> 01:59:45,635
Bukan soal angka nol...

967
01:59:45,799 --> 01:59:46,831
...atau satu...

968
01:59:46,995 --> 01:59:48,470
...atau kode.

969
01:59:48,623 --> 01:59:49,751
Menurutmu itu apa?

970
01:59:49,911 --> 01:59:51,309
Minggir!

971
01:59:51,463 --> 01:59:52,961
Aku seorang pemain.

972
01:59:53,125 --> 01:59:55,462
Kusewa orang untuk
